{"tid":2443606,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"文匯 : 《理大圍城》有違反國安法的明顯嫌疑，促請電檢處「依法禁播」!","createTime":"2021-03-12T07:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T07:34:37.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb11022d4b9714ae72632a9e24174fad8fabe9e0","tid":2443606,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"《文匯》狙擊 促禁播《理大圍城》<br />\n<br />\n六部得獎電影巡禮作品中，《理大圍城》過去曾於香港藝術中心播出，惟一直未有商業影院願意放映。高先電影院勢成首間播放《理大圍城》的商營戲院。<br />\n<br />\n高先電影院宣佈放映《理大圍城》翌日，《文匯報》發表題為「《理大圍城》煽暴違法必須禁播」的社評文章，指該片「美化反修例黑暴」，「煽動對抗警方和特區政府，散播仇視國家情緒」。全片大篇幅記錄嚴重犯罪行為，包含青少年使用具殺傷力武器的鏡頭，不單意識不良，更「有違反《電影檢查條例》及香港國安法的明顯嫌疑」，促請電檢處「依法禁播該片，以免顛倒是非、荼毒社會。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E9%AB%98%E5%85%88%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E9%99%A2-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E-%E5%8A%A0%E5%A0%B4-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E8%BC%AA%E5%80%99%E5%B7%B2%E5%94%AE%E7%BD%84-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF-%E4%BF%83%E9%9B%BB%E6%AA%A2%E8%99%95-%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E6%92%AD/?fbclid=IwAR1wyu8vGPJ30OriZKTe0WBXRs8LvnvFK8_8zH9bdmV0Xbb43O08CQAk9uI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2585%2588%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%259F%258E-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%2599%25A8%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%2594%25AE%25E7%25BD%2584-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E8%2599%2595-%25E4%25BE%259D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%2592%25AD%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1wyu8vGPJ30OriZKTe0WBXRs8LvnvFK8_8zH9bdmV0Xbb43O08CQAk9uI&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw5j7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=57096bec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2585%2588%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%259F%25